# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Energy Forecast PT — frontend environment variables
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (git-ignored) and adjust as needed.
# Only variables prefixed with `VITE_` are exposed to the browser by Vite.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Base URL of the FastAPI backend.
#
# - Leave UNSET (or empty) to use the Vite dev proxy defined in vite.config.ts,
#   which forwards requests from `/api/*` to `http://localhost:8000/*`.
#   This is the recommended default for `npm run dev` / `npm run preview`.
#
# - Set to an absolute URL to hit the backend directly (useful for production
#   builds, or when the frontend is served from a different origin than the
#   FastAPI server).
#
# Examples:
#   VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
#   VITE_API_URL=https://api.energy-forecast.example.com
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
